{"type": "article", "id": 20420, "title": "多功能书桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-08T07:30:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 52, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122334rcdgfwykn7hYtOMp.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这张书桌拥有各种适应现代人生活的“机关”，桌面有放手机的凹槽，桌面的右侧是写草稿的白板，还有放插线板的卡槽，挂耳机的挂钩，固定插线的夹子。桌子的整体造型是细长而轻盈的，即便有这些功能也不会显得杂乱。此外，桌子的高度也可以调整，售价 2350 美元起，<a href=\"http://www.ideapaint.com/products/artifox\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122332xgn3RIip6hdPmuZS.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.55733333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122332GarpYXn4MQEKUzSl.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122332mrZiOc3xA6KR0M7b.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122333OszcIVRgfHS3hCyv.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071223337Bz6bAXkdgOoPtK8.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}